# Shortbread Biscuits

Makes 12

## Ingredients

* 375g flour
* 250g butter
* 125g caster sugar
* pnch salt

## Method

1. Mix, roll, cut, prick with fork for even cooking
2. Baking tray
3. Bake 160c ~20m

## Notes
